  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is designed to compare the efficacy and safety of two-weekly RAILIRI regimen with
      FOLFIRI regimen in the treatment of advanced colorectal cancer patients in the second-line
      setting.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
